  "tips": [
    "A refuge where you can sleep, have a picnic, barbecue.\nSuitable for mountain biking, walking or driving.",
    "The Cumbre de Pla de Pujalts, also known as Costa Pubilla is a 2,056m mountain that is located between the municipalities of Gombrèn, Planoles and Toses, in the Ripollès region. It is part of the Montgrony mountain range",
    "Collado at 1716m of height located just above the town of Planoles and which serves as a foot access to the Sierra del Montgrony and to the top of the Costa Pubilla.",
    "Forest refuge within the municipality of Campelles (Ripollès) at an altitude of 1,769m. It is located under the northern slope of the La Covil peak. It consists of 2 separate rooms, an open area for cattle and a part with a door, with a fireplace, table and wooden bunks. It is a rather precarious unguarded shelter."
  ],
